작성: 2026-05-08
구동: 사용자 directive `/loop 5m keep going` cron `34b18744` + `all fire bg` parallel batch

본 file 은 disease-axis-orthogonal roadmap. hexa-bio 의 5 axis 가 environmental medicine (환경의학 — exogenous + chronic + population-level exposure 기반 disease) 에 어떻게 기여하는지 cross-axis mapping + 신규 약물 기준 falsifier inventory.

(Distinct from `.roadmap.disease_toxicology` — toxicology 는 drug overdose + iatrogenic 중심; environmental_health = exogenous + chronic + population-level exposure 중심. 농도 낮으나 만성 + 광역 인구 + 정책 중심 차이.)

scope:
- 중금속 중독 chelation (Pb / As / Hg / Fe / Cu — succimer / penicillamine / dimercaprol / EDTA / deferoxamine cross-toxicology)
- air pollution PM2.5 / ozone-induced disease (cardiopulmonary mortality + COPD exacerbation — cross-pulmonology / cross-cardiology)
- 라돈 (Rn-222) 노출 lung 손상 (US 폐암 2nd 원인 — cross-cancer / cross-pulmonology)
- 오염물질-driven cancer (asbestos mesothelioma / benzene leukemia / formaldehyde nasopharyngeal — cross-cancer)
- 농약 / 살충제 organophosphate poisoning 응급 (pralidoxime 2-PAM + atropine — cross-toxicology)
- 라디오 방사선 노출 protection (potassium iodide KI / amifostine — Fukushima 2011 lessons)
- heat-related illness (cooling + dantrolene if MH crossover — cross-critical_care)
- cold-related illness (hypothermia + frostbite)
- climate-driven infectious vector expansion (dengue / Zika / Chikungunya / Lyme 북상 — cross-infectious)
- water-quality (PFAS endocrine disruption / Pb water — cross-endocrine)
- e-waste 중금속 + lithium battery exposure
- microplastic / nanoplastic 신경독성 research (no clinical Tx)
- BPA / phthalate endocrine disruption (cross-endocrine / cross-reproductive)
- indoor air (mold + VOC + secondhand smoke — cross-pulmonology)

